\toprule
Scenario & Staleness P95 & Duplicate Proposals & Audit Completeness \\
\midrule
Rename burst (200 ops) & 182 ms & 0.9\% & 100\% \\
Rewrite storm (1,000 ops) & 236 ms & 1.3\% & 100\% \\
Delete/restore loop & 205 ms & 0.0\% & 100\% \\
\bottomrule
